Package gameClient

Class match

java.lang.Object
gameClient.match
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.util.Comparator<match>
public class match
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.util.Comparator<match>
This Class represents a Match between a Pokemon and an Agent that chases after the Pokemon The class was created for an algorithm that matches between agents and pokemons in an efficient way The class calculate time for agent getting to a pokemon, and check how worth it comparing to chasing another pokemon
